-- Russia’s Budget Deficit May Reach 1.5% of GDP by 2015, RIA Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-06-07T17:13:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/russia-s-budget-deficit-may-reach-1-5-of-gdp-by-2015-ria-says.html
Russia’s budget deficit may reach 1.5
percent of gross domestic product by 2015, more than previously
estimated,  RIA Novosti  reported, citing a revised forecast by
the  Economy Ministry .  To contact the reporter on this story:
